Tuesday Thoughts...
-------------------

* CBS reads the fine
print: An amusing subplot has surfaced in Trump=E2=80=99s lawsuit over 60 M=
inutes=E2=80=99 Kamala Harris interview. While lawyers for CBS have announc=
ed their intention to dig into Trump=E2=80=99s personal finances, they are =
also gesturing at another legal strategy that will be relatable to anyone w=
ho=E2=80=99s ever signed up for a streaming service: CBS wants to know if t=
he president and his co-plaintiff are Paramount+ or YouTube subscribers.

